      a baby seal?</font>

348
00:14:24,730 --> 00:14:26,490
<font face="Serif" size="18">That is not fair.</font>

349
00:14:26,490 --> 00:14:28,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's it, Klaus!</font>

350
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:30,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is the moment she realized
        life wasn't fair.</font>

351
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:31,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's her trigger.</font>

352
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then we need
to recreate it.</font>

353
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">That will snap her out
  of the deep trance.</font>

354
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:37,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's go.</font>

355
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:40,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">KLAUS: That Joe Chandler was
           a cool dude.</font>

356
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,540
<font face="Serif" size="18">Next time...</font>

357
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:44,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">Next time I'll have bullets.</font>

358
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:49,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">(crickets chirping)</font>

359
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:51,990
<font face="Serif" size="18">(lowered voice) Jeff,
 I love the symmetry of this.</font>

360
00:14:51,990 --> 00:14:53,890
<font face="Serif" size="18">Seeing a seal clubbed
       to death</font>

361
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:56,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">is what broke happy Hayley
      the first time,</font>

362
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:58,990
<font face="Serif" size="18">and doing it again
will break her once more.</font>

363
00:14:58,990 --> 00:15:01,490
<font face="Serif" size="18">Klaus, we're not gonna
          club a seal to death.</font>

364
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're right. It doesn't
    have to be a seal.</font>

365
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:05,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just anything innocent.</font>

366
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:09,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">The important thing
 is the club...and the death.</font>

367
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:13,510
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, 'cause that's what turned
   her into frowny-faced Hayley.</font>

368
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:16,340
<font face="Serif" size="18">If we can just show her that
  the world is unfair to animals</font>

369
00:15:16,340 --> 00:15:19,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">without murdering one, then
    maybe she'll snap out of it,</font>

370
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:22,620
<font face="Serif" size="18">but keep a little bit
         of happy Hayley inside.</font>

371
00:15:22,620 --> 00:15:24,780
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh,<i> sucks.</i></font>

372
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,450
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought we were
 on the same page</font>

373
00:15:26,450 --> 00:15:28,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">the whole drive.</font>

374
00:15:30,190 --> 00:15:32,430
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are we
                at the fish zoo?</font>

375
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:34,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, just for fun.</font>

376
00:15:34,130 --> 00:15:36,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, look at
        the pretty seals!</font>

377
00:15:36,970 --> 00:15:38,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait a minute.</font>

378
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:41,430
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's an awfully small place
       for a seal to live.</font>

379
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:44,370
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not fair.
          Right, Klaus?</font>

380
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:45,810
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, yeah.</font>

381
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:49,740
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look at these poor,
     sweet, gentle creatures.</font>

382
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:53,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">The lambs of the sea,
     stuck their whole lives</font>

383
00:15:53,210 --> 00:15:55,050
<font face="Serif" size="18">in a tiny...</font>

384
00:15:55,050 --> 00:15:56,780
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's one behind me,
           isn't there?</font>

385
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:58,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">And is it, like,
       exactly the opposite</font>

386
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">of how I described them?</font>

387
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:02,390
<font face="Serif" size="18">(growls)
              Aah!</font>

388
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:05,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">Klaus!
          Aah! Help me!</font>

389
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold on!</font>

390
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:09,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ohh! (panting)</font>

391
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:11,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">In your face, seal.
              You can't get me.</font>

392
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:12,630
<font face="Serif" size="18">(growls)
                            Aah!</font>

393
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:14,630
<font face="Serif" size="18">Seals can come on land?</font>

394
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:17,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought they had to stay
       in the water like fish!</font>

395
00:16:17,110 --> 00:16:19,810
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no. (gasps)</font>

396
00:16:19,810 --> 00:16:23,440
<font face="Serif" size="18">Evolve, Klaus. (gasps)
          Evolve like the wind!</font>

397
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:26,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">(grunts) Ow! Aah!</font>

398
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:28,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">(growls)
Hey! (grunts)</font>

399
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:32,750
<font face="Serif" size="18">(growling)</font>

400
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:36,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">(barking)
Stay...away...from Klaus!</font>

401
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,420
<font face="Serif" size="18">(panting)</font>

402
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:41,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ooh! You killed it.</font>

403
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:42,800
<font face="Serif" size="18">I want a mermaid key chain!</font>

404
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:45,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, good, she didn't see me
       kill the seal.</font>

405
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:46,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">(click)</font>

406
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:48,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">But<i> we</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> did.</font>

407
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:50,170
<font face="Serif" size="18">(timer dings)</font>

408
00:16:50,170 --> 00:16:53,010
<font face="Serif" size="18">We did it, friends.
   We cooked the perfect pork.</font>

409
00:16:53,010 --> 00:16:56,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wish you could try it,
       but you're all dead.</font>

410
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:04,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">(screaming)</font>

411
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:07,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">(gasps) Oh, God!</font>

412
00:17:07,820 --> 00:17:10,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">The meaning of the dream
           is so clear!</font>

413
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:13,890
<font face="Serif" size="18">I gotta share this pork
   with my friends immediately!</font>

414
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:17,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, come on. Every morning?
       Didn't you hear me?</font>

415
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's no time. I need
      to do the right thing</font>

416
00:17:19,470 --> 00:17:21,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">for my friends.</font>

417
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:24,240
<font face="Serif" size="18">You should be
  in that slow cooker, you pig.</font>

418
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,080
<font face="Serif" size="18">(remote control clicks)</font>

419
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:32,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">I know that's hard
                  to watch.</font>

420
00:17:32,550 --> 00:17:35,080
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's why I only showed it
           to you 10 times.</font>

421
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:37,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jeff Fischer broke
              into the aquarium</font>

422
00:17:37,820 --> 00:17:41,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">and brutally killed a seal,
        but not just any seal.</font>

423
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:43,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">This was Harpy...</font>

424
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:44,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">(remote control clicks)
             ...the cutest seal.</font>

425
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:46,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">JURY: Aw.</font>

426
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:47,430
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't hear you!</font>

427
00:17:47,430 --> 00:17:49,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">JURY (louder): Aw!</font>

428
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:52,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">The prosecution rests,
   but not before a quick round</font>

429
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:54,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">of high five
     with this awesome jury!</font>

430
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:58,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">(cheers and applause,
   upbeat theme music playing)</font>

431
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:01,670
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's happening, daddy?</font>

432
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:05,080
<font face="Serif" size="18">That man is on trial because
  he did a bad thing to a seal.</font>

433
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:07,950
<font face="Serif" size="18">I like seals.
 I don't like that man.</font>

434
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:09,880
<font face="Serif" size="18">No one does.
         (gavel bangs)</font>

435
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, does the defendant
      want to waste our time</font>

436
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">before the jury
        finds him guilty?</font>

437
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:16,090
<font face="Serif" size="18">We'd like to call
       Dr. Penguin to the stand.</font>

438
00:18:16,090 --> 00:18:17,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">Huh?
       Who's Dr. Penguin?</font>

439
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,190
<font face="Serif" size="18">That'd be me.</font>

440
00:18:19,190 --> 00:18:21,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can explain why Jeff
             did what he did,</font>

441
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:25,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">or if I may hypnotize
           the jury, your honor?</font>

442
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, fun! I'll allow it.</font>

443
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:31,800
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jeff Fischer is not guilty.</font>

444
00:18:31,810 --> 00:18:35,240
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not guilty. With every swing
          of the watch,</font>

445
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:39,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">you'll find Jeff
      a little less guilty.</font>

446
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:41,980
<font face="Serif" size="18">We find the defendant
     not guilty.</font>

447
00:18:41,980 --> 00:18:43,480
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, cool.</font>

448
00:18:43,490 --> 00:18:45,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jeff Fischer, you're free to go.
         (gavel bangs)</font>

449
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes!
  (gallery shouting at once)</font>

450
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:48,620
<font face="Serif" size="18">Daddy, what's wrong?</font>

451
00:18:48,620 --> 00:18:50,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">The man who killed the seal
           is being let go.</font>

452
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:54,390
<font face="Serif" size="18">What?! But that's not fair!
      That's not fair.</font>

453
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,800
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's not fair.
  (gruff voice) That's not fair.</font>

454
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">(clears throat)</font>

455
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">(normal voice)
     That's not fair.</font>

456
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:02,070
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh. Whoa.
    Where the hell am I?</font>

457
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:03,570
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh. Hayley's back.</font>

458
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:05,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hayley! I've missed you
        so much.</font>

459
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:08,070
<font face="Serif" size="18">Missed me?
      But where have I been?</font>

460
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:10,940
<font face="Serif" size="18">The real question is
 <i> when</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> have you been?</font>

461
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:13,450
<font face="Serif" size="18">(laughter)</font>

462
00:19:13,450 --> 00:19:15,950
<font face="Serif" size="18">Seriously, guys, I can't account
       for a lot of time,</font>

463
00:19:15,950 --> 00:19:17,620
<font face="Serif" size="18">and I'm kind of freaking out.</font>

464
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:19,750
<font face="Serif" size="18">Will someone please explain
        what's happening?</font>

465
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:22,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">More like,<i> who's</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> happening,
        right, guys?</font>

466
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:25,990
<font face="Serif" size="18">(laughter)</font>

467
00:19:25,990 --> 00:19:27,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">(crickets chirping)</font>

468
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:29,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">Guys, I'm sorry I got
           carried away</font>

469
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">with the slow cooker,</font>

470
00:19:31,670 --> 00:19:33,670
<font face="Serif" size="18">but my pursuit of perfection
     was not totally in vain,</font>

471
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:35,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">'cause like the pork,</font>

472
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:37,540
<font face="Serif" size="18">our friendship has been
     simmered to perfection.</font>

473
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:39,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's eat!</font>

474
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,510
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mmm. Mmm.</font>

475
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:42,880
<font face="Serif" size="18">Divine.</font>

476
00:19:45,210 --> 00:19:48,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yet it leaves
        something behind.</font>

477
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:49,980
<font face="Serif" size="18">Metallic, maybe?</font>

478
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:53,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">Furry.
                  Almost moving?</font>

479
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:56,490
<font face="Serif" size="18">With perhaps
maggoty undertones?</font>

480
00:19:56,490 --> 00:19:59,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">(siren wailing)</font>

481
00:19:59,290 --> 00:20:00,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who gave you
the stupid idea</font>

482
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:03,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">you could eat
 12-day-old pork?</font>

483
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">He did!</font>

484
00:20:06,900 --> 00:20:08,870
<font face="Serif" size="18">(snorting)</font>

485
00:20:08,870 --> 00:20:12,240
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's pigs! He's pigs!</font>

486
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:14,640
<font face="Serif" size="18">(grunts)
 I gotta restrain this one.</font>

487
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:17,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's on to us.</font>

488
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:19,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">This isn't an ambulance!</font>

489
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:21,880
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's a goddamn hambulance!</font>

490
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:23,750
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i> (snorting alarm wailing)</i></font>

491
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">(gasping)</font>

492
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:27,590
<font face="Serif" size="18">Pigs. Pigs everywhere.</font>

493
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:29,220
<font face="Serif" size="18">They're all pigs.</font>

494
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think Steve ate
a lot more than us.</font>

495
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:32,260
<font face="Serif" size="18">(grunting)</font>

496
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:37,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thanks for looking out
              for me, Jeff.</font>

497
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,500
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm glad to be back
               to my old self,</font>

498
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:41,100
<font face="Serif" size="18">even if happy Hayley
             is gone for good.</font>

499
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:43,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's all right, babe.
 I love you no matter what.</font>

500
00:20:43,840 --> 00:20:45,910
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, wanna grab a bite
 before the P.E.T.A. protest?</font>

501
00:20:45,910 --> 00:20:47,870
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sure. For some reason,</font>

502
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:50,340
<font face="Serif" size="18">I could go for a scoop
              of mint chip.</font>

503
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:54,580
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey! You're smiling, babe.
That's one for the scrapbook.</font>

504
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:57,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">(camera shutter clicks,
              whirs)</font>

505
00:20:57,720 --> 00:21:00,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">(whispers) I hate this part.</font>

506
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:04,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bye! Have a beautiful time!</font>

507
00:21:06,190 --> 00:21:08,030
